5
00:03:05,409 --> 00:03:06,410
LUKA

6
00:03:06,619 --> 00:03:07,620
KESAKITAN

7
00:03:07,787 --> 00:03:08,788
PENDERITAAN

8
00:03:08,997 --> 00:03:10,123
CINTAILAH

9
00:03:47,535 --> 00:03:48,954
