Kakinya patah waktu turun.
Dia menjilati...

1112
01:38:52,741 --> 01:38:54,743
Jangan sakiti anjingku!

1113
01:38:54,952 --> 01:38:56,870
Jangan paksa aku menyakiti anjingmu!

1114
01:38:57,036 --> 01:38:59,205
Kau belum tahu rasanya sakit!

1115
01:39:04,628 --> 01:39:08,214
Ambilkan aku telepon
atau kubunuh dia!

1116
01:39:12,761 --> 01:39:16,974
- Sial!
- Ambilkan aku telepon!

1117
01:39:17,181 --> 01:39:19,308
Akan kulakukan, Tuan!

1118
01:39:19,475 --> 01:39:23,562
Akan kupatahkan lehernya!

1119
01:39:24,022 --> 01:39:26,024
Baiklah, Tuan. Sedang kulakukan!

1120
01:39:49,631 --> 01:39:51,842
Baiklah, aku datang.

1121
01:39:53,259 --> 01:39:54,636
Kami akan masuk.

1122
01:39:59,473 --> 01:40:01,685
Selamat siang. Maaf mengganggu.

1123
01:40:01,893 --> 01:40:04,186
Aku mencari keluarga Ny. Lippman.

1124
01:40:04,855 --> 01:40:06,940
FBI! Semuanya menunduk!

1125
01:40:07,941 --> 01:40:09,860
Keluarga Lippman
tidak tinggal di sini lagi.

1126
01:40:10,068 --> 01:40:12,528
Permisi, Pak.
Aku perlu bantuanmu.

1127
01:40:13,739 --> 01:40:15,489
- Aman!
- Aman!

1128
01:40:16,282 --> 01:40:18,326
Ada masalah apa?

1129
01:40:18,534 --> 01:40:21,245
Aku sedang menyelidiki
kematian Fredrica Bimmel.

1130
01:40:24,582 --> 01:40:26,043
Di sini tak ada orang, Jack.

1131
01:40:28,837 --> 01:40:30,047
Clarice.

1132
01:40:30,254 --> 01:40:31,422
Namamu...?

1133
01:40:31,630 --> 01:40:32,758
Jack Gordon.

1134
01:40:32,966 --> 01:40:34,843
Tn. Gordon. Bagus.

1135
01:40:35,010 --> 01:40:38,262
Fredrica bekerja untuk Ny. Lippman.
Kau mengenalnya?

1136
01:40:39,221 --> 01:40:40,891
Tidak.

1137
01:40:41,474 --> 01:40:42,934
Tunggu.

1138
01:40:43,225 --> 01:40:45,436
Dia orangnya gendut?

1139
01:40:46,395 --> 01:40:48,023
Ya, dia gendut, Pak.

1140
01:40:48,230 --> 01:40:49,732
Ya, aku mungkin...

1141
01:40:49,940 --> 01:40:52,442
Tidak, kubaca tentang dia di koran.

1142
01:40:54,235 --> 01:40:56,613
Ny. Lippman punya seorang putra.
Mungkin dia bisa bantu.

1143
01:40:56,822 --> 01:40:58,573
Aku punya alamatnya di sini.

1144
01:40:58,741 --> 01:40:59,992
Kau mau masuk?

1145
01:41:00,200 --> 01:41:01,284
- Bolehkah?
- Tentu.

1146
01:41:01,493 --> 01:41:02,660
Terima kasih.

1147
01:41:21,471 --> 01:41:23,556
Kau hampir menangkap seseorang?

1148
01:41:25,308 --> 01:41:26,309
Ya.

1149
01:41:26,518 --> 01:41:27,728
Mungkin.

1150
01:41:29,562 --> 01:41:30,773
Apa kau

1151
01:41:31,689 --> 01:41:35,276
mengambil alih rumah ini
setelah Ny. Lippman mati?

1152
01:41:36,569 --> 01:41:40,908
Ya, kubeli rumah ini dua tahun lalu.

1153
01:41:42,200 --> 01:41:45,578
Apa dia tinggalkan dokumen bisnis

1154
01:41:45,788 --> 01:41:49,624
formulir pajak, daftar pegawai?

1155
01:41:50,250 --> 01:41:52,169
Sama sekali tidak.

1156
01:41:54,546 --> 01:41:57,298
Jadi, apa FBI tahu sesuatu?

1157
01:41:57,507 --> 01:42:00,886
Polisi tampaknya
tak punya petunjuk apa pun.

1158
01:42:10,437 --> 01:42:15,151
Apa kau punya deskripsi fisiknya,
sidik jari, atau semacamnya?

1159
01:42:16,568 --> 01:42:17,610
Tidak.

1160
01:42:20,238 --> 01:42:21,573
Kami tak punya.

1161
01:42:32,960 --> 01:42:34,419
Ini nomer teleponnya.

1162
01:42:35,921 --> 01:42:37,589
Bagus sekali, Tn. Gordon.

1163
01:42:37,798 --> 01:42:39,632
Boleh kupinjam teleponmu?

1164
01:42:47,808 --> 01:42:49,852
Tentu.

1165
01:42:51,352 --> 01:42:52,520
Jangan bergerak!

1166
01:42:53,354 --> 01:42:57,442
Angkat tanganmu dan berbaliklah.
Rentangkan kakimu.

1167
01:42:58,568 --> 01:42:59,862
Rentangkan kakimu!

1168
01:43:00,070 --> 01:43:01,779
Taruh tanganmu di punggung...

1169
01:43:01,989 --> 01:43:03,448
Jangan bergerak!

1170
01:44:16,020 --> 01:44:18,022
Hei!

1171
01:44:37,959 --> 01:44:40,295
Kau ada di sana?

1172
01:44:41,670 --> 01:44:44,840
Aku di bawah sini!

1173
01:45:04,068 --> 01:45:05,694
Catherine Martin?

1174
01:45:05,902 --> 01:45:07,238
Ya!

1175
01:45:08,948 --> 01:45:10,241
FBI.

1176
01:45:10,407 --> 01:45:11,700
Kau aman.

1177
01:45:11,908 --> 01:45:14,870
Aku tak merasa aman!
Keluarkan aku dari sini!

1178
01:45:29,969 --> 01:45:31,845
Kau baik-baik saja. Mana dia?

1179
01:45:32,055 --> 01:45:35,016
Aku tak peduli.
Keluarkan aku dari sini!

1180
01:45:35,224 --> 01:45:38,394
Catherine, kau harus tenang!
Diamkan anjing itu!

1181
01:45:38,602 --> 01:45:40,646
Keluarkan aku dari sini!

1182
01:45:41,772 --> 01:45:42,939
Ya, Tuhan.

1183
01:45:45,360 --> 01:45:49,446
Catherine, kau akan kubebaskan.
Namun, kini, dengar aku.

1184
01:45:49,655 --> 01:45:51,991
Aku harus pergi.
Aku segera kembali.

1185
01:45:52,200 --> 01:45:55,869
Jangan tinggalkan aku. Sialan! Jangan!

1186
01:45:56,079 --> 01:45:57,621
Jangan tinggalkan aku!

1187
01:45:57,829 --> 01:46:00,540
Pria ini benar-benar gila!

1188
01:46:02,918 --> 01:46:07,756
Tunggu! Aku harus keluar dari sini!

1189
01:46:09,258 --> 01:46:10,259
Kumohon!

1190
01:46:10,467 --> 01:46:15,138
Catherine! Polisi lain
sebentar lagi akan tiba.

1191
01:46:15,347 --> 01:46:19,101
Tunggu! Jangan pergi! Kumohon!

1192
01:46:19,267 --> 01:46:20,601
Diamlah!

1193
01:46:22,895 --> 01:46:25,440
Ya, Tuhan!

1194
01:49:49,393 --> 01:49:50,935
TEROR!

1195
01:49:51,144 --> 01:49:53,439
BILL MENGULITI GADIS KELIMA

1196
01:50:21,215 --> 01:50:23,677
- Kau baik-baik saja?
- Hanya serbuk mesiu. Aku baik.

1197
01:50:23,885 --> 01:50:26,930
Agen Starling, bagaimana kau tahu
Buffalo Bill ada di sini?

1198
01:50:27,138 --> 01:50:30,808
DEPARTEMEN KEHAKIMAN
BIRO PENYELIDIK FEDERAL

1199
01:50:33,227 --> 01:50:36,105
Clarice M. Starling.

1200
01:50:38,232 --> 01:50:39,568
Selamat.

1201
01:50:53,122 --> 01:50:55,875
Ernest W. Stevens.

1202
01:51:02,591 --> 01:51:03,717
DEPARTEMEN KEHAKIMAN
FBI

1203
01:51:13,935 --> 01:51:15,812
Agen Khusus Starling!

1204
01:51:16,229 --> 01:51:18,147
- Agen Khusus Mapp.
- Ada telepon.

1205
01:51:18,315 --> 01:51:19,650
Terima kasih. Permisi.

1206
01:51:19,857 --> 01:51:21,150
Starling.

1207
01:51:23,945 --> 01:51:26,823
Pilch, tolong foto kami berdua.

1208
01:51:27,073 --> 01:51:28,116
Baik.

1209
01:51:30,076 --> 01:51:32,203
Aku hanya ingin mengucapkan selamat.

1210
01:51:32,579 --> 01:51:36,123
Aku tak begitu suka pesta,
jadi aku akan pulang.

1211
01:51:36,582 --> 01:51:38,250
Baik. Silakan.

1212
01:51:39,752 --> 01:51:41,379
Terima kasih, Pak Crawford.

1213
01:51:49,177 --> 01:51:51,431
Hari ini ayahmu pasti bangga.

1214
01:51:54,726 --> 01:51:56,477
Jangan lupa ada telepon untukmu.

1215
01:52:01,106 --> 01:52:02,483
Starling.

1216
01:52:02,775 --> 01:52:04,360
Clarice,

1217
01:52:04,901 --> 01:52:07,405
dombanya sudah berhenti berteriak?

1218
01:52:07,821 --> 01:52:08,947
Dr. Lecter?

1219
01:52:09,156 --> 01:52:12,200
Tak perlu repot-repot melacakku.
Aku tak akan lama.

1220
01:52:15,705 --> 01:52:17,831
Kau di mana, Dr. Lecter?

1221
01:52:18,040 --> 01:52:19,916
Aku tak punya rencana
untuk mengunjungimu.

1222
01:52:20,083 --> 01:52:22,545
Dunia lebih menarik
dengan kau di dalamnya.

1223
01:52:23,086 --> 01:52:26,089
Jaga dirimu dan jangan mencariku.

1224
01:52:26,298 --> 01:52:28,842
Kau tahu aku tak bisa penuhi janji itu.

1225
01:52:29,301 --> 01:52:31,679
Kuharap kita bisa mengobrol lebih lama,

1226
01:52:32,971 --> 01:52:35,683
tetapi teman lamaku akan datang
untuk makan malam.

1227
01:52:37,142 --> 01:52:38,394
Dah.

1228
01:52:38,852 --> 01:52:40,187
Dr. Lecter!

1229
01:52:42,690 --> 01:52:44,149
Dr. Lecter.

1230
01:52:46,318 --> 01:52:47,779
Dr. Lecter.

1231
01:52:49,739 --> 01:52:51,281
Dr. Lecter?

1232
01:52:52,324 --> 01:52:53,743
Permisi. Maaf.

1233
01:52:53,950 --> 01:52:55,578
Sistem keamanannya sudah diaktifkan?

1234
01:52:55,787 --> 01:52:58,456
- Sistem keamanan di sini hebat.
- Kuhargai itu.

1235
01:57:57,377 --> 01:58:04,258
DIPERSEMBAHKAN UNTUK TREY WILSON

